{
  "stem": "11179.1",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 4.0,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So we made a living.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "A-- a bare living, but we made a living.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I'm not complaining.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Still, we were not short of food.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "We had a roof over our head, and we had clothes to wear, so I mean-- so my father did work, keeping busy.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "He worked there voluntarily, and it kept him busy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then they learned-- my parents learned for-- he tried to-- he tried to leave.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "He wrote to relatives, he wrote to people we knew.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "No dice.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "You're over 35 and you don't know a trade, we don't want you.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "That was the consulate answer.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And relatives-- distant relatives, they promised everything, kept nothing.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "They were mostly relatives I didn't know.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "My-- they were cousins of my grandmother, for instance, here in the United States.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And they promised everything.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 36,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "Didn't do anything.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, immediately, but particularly when-- when-- when I had to leave school.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I enjoyed school.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I had no problem in that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "As a matter of fact, two older kids I knew from playground, [INAUDIBLE] they said, if ever anybody-- and both were belonged to the Hitler Youth-- they said, if ever anybody gives you any trouble, let us know in that school.",
      "word_count": 41
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "They went-- they went to that school.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 37,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "They were two or three years older than I.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh yeah, they did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They-- they had to.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They had to, just about.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You couldn't [INAUDIBLE] except it.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I had a good, good friend, and my mother was very friendly with a-- with a kid from-- I knew from elementary school.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 38,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she told us already, right away in the beginning, I put my son into a-- there was a-- The boy scouts, I think, were out by that time.",
      "word_count": 29
    }
  ],
